CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772374275
OL,3,CCabinet Office minister Josh Simons
OL,4,Cresigns over Labour Together
OL,5,C'distraction'
OL,7,FA Labour MP has resigned as a Cabinet
OL,8,FOffice minister after an investigation
OL,9,Finto allegations a prominent think
OL,10,Ftank he ran before entering government
OL,11,Fpaid for a probe into journalists.
OL,13,FAlthough the investigation by Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer's ethics adviser found Josh
OL,15,FSimons had not breached the
OL,16,FMinisterial Code, the MP for
OL,17,FMakerfield, in Wigan, said he had
OL,18,F"become a distraction from this
OL,19,FGovernment's important work".
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
